/**
 * SkyGate — App Controller v2
 *
 * Key improvements over v1:
 * - Compact floor control (popover) replaces 4-button strip
 * - Per-floor pan/zoom state (no reset on switch)
 * - SVG memoization — re-renders only when floor or route changes
 * - Semantic step grouping (hides corridor/waypoint graph noise)
 * - 3-state bottom sheet (collapsed / half / full)
 * - Floating navigation instruction card in nav mode
 * - "Return to route" control after manual floor exploration
 * - Separated map state from form state for targeted re-renders
 */

